## Last updated: 18/10/2024

At Text Repeater, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information when you use the Text Repeater app, which allows users to generate repeated text, copy it, and share it with others.

### 1. Information We Collect

The Text Repeater app does not collect any personal data or sensitive information from users. No registration or login is required to use the app’s core functionalities. The app operates locally on your device and does not access or store personal data.

### 2. How We Use Information

Since the Text Repeater app does not collect any personal information, we do not store, use, or share any user data. The app only provides the following functionalities:

Generating repeated text based on user input.
Copying the repeated text to your device’s clipboard.
Sharing the generated text via third-party apps (e.g., messaging, social media) based on the user’s action.

### 3. Data Sharing

As the Text Repeater app does not collect or store any personal information, we do not share any personal data with third parties.

### 4. Third-Party Services

If you choose to share generated text using third-party apps (e.g., messaging or social media platforms), please note that these third-party apps may collect data as per their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any third-party services you use through the Text Repeater app.

### 5. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in the app or applicable laws. When we make changes, we will update the "Last updated" date at the top of this policy. Continued use of the Text Repeater app following changes to the policy will signify your acceptance of those changes.

### 6. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please feel free to contact us at sajjad.ashiq1n@gmail.com.
